m; text-align: left; line-height: 2em;\">2</p></td><td width=\"254\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-right: 1px solid black; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin: 15px 3px 15px 5px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;\">临床医学、重症医学及相关专</p></td></tr><tr style=\";height:47px\"><td width=\"647\" colspan=\"5\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black; border-left: 1px solid black; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px 15px 4px; text-align: left; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\">备注：标“<span>*</span>”为紧缺专业，在不超过专业基地容量的情况下，可以根据实际情况</p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px 15px 4px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em;\">适当超计划招录。</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">三、培养年限及要求：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>1.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\">医院按照国家卫健委《住院医师规范化培训的内容与标准（试行）》和江苏省卫健委住院医师规范化培训的相关要求，制定培训计划和轮转方案，并严格按照计划对培训学员进行培训。 </span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>2.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\">住院医师规范化培训时长根据《住院医师规范化培训的内容与标准（试行）》，培训年限为三年，学员完成培训并通过各项考核者，颁发国家级《住院医师规范化培训合格证书》。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>3.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\">住培学员在我院培训期间，须履行国家规定的住院医师规范化培训期间应尽的责任和义务，并遵守医院相关管理规定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">四、盐城市一院住培基地学员的优惠政策：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>1.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">我院于<span>2019</span>年正式挂牌南京大学医学院附属盐城第一人民医院，根据盐城市政府与南京大学合作协议，凡在我院参培的住培学员可择优参加南京大学在职研究生班，结业时通过南京大学在职研究生班各项考核合格可获得“<strong>南京大学研究生</strong>”学位证。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>2.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">我院全科专业基地为盐城市最大的全科培训基地，盐城市全科医学会主任委员、盐城市全科医学研究所均在基地，多次举办省市级学术会议、师资培训、继续教育；为进一步建设全科培训基地，提高教学水平，除增加师资培训，提升基层实践基地水平外，给以全科进一步倾斜支持，包含：提高学员补助、配置导师、专项技能培训等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>3.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">我院招收的社会化学员结业后需自行择业，根据双向选择原则，毕业时考核优秀、紧缺专业的学员同等条件下我院优先录用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>五、</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">相关规定及待遇</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（一）根据《关于贯彻落实住院医师规范化培训“<strong><strong>两个同等对待</strong></strong>”政策的通知》（国卫办科教〔</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">2021</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">〕</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">18</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">号）的要求，维护学员权益，落实“两个同等对待”政策，面向社会招收的普通高校应届毕业生培训对象培训合格当年在医疗卫生机构就业的，在招聘、派遣、落户等方面，按当年应届毕业生同等对待。对经住培合格的本科学历临床医师，在人员招聘、职称晋升、岗位聘用、薪酬待遇等方面与临床医学、中医专业学位硕士研究生同等对待。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（二）医院按照国家卫健委《住院医师规范化培训的内容与标准（</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">2022</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">年版）》和江苏省卫健委住院医师规范化培训的相关要求进行轮转培训。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（三）培训年限为三年。完成培训任务，并通过结业考核者，由省卫健委颁发全国统一制式的《住院医师规范化培训合格证书》。进入培训后，因个人原因需要协议退培的，培训时长不得少于一年。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（四）委托培训学员在培训期间原人事（劳动）、工资关系不变，委托培训学员的基本工资、基础性绩效及各种社会保险仍由原单位发放。社会化学员基本工资、绩效工资及相关保险发放标准参照我院同等条件住院医师工资水平。</span><span style=\"background: white;\">社会化学员第一年实发工资约<span>5.1</span>万，五险一金及补助、绩效另算，绩效根据是否取得执医资格和工作能力表现，每年<span>2.6</span>万<span>-4</span>万，</span><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">年收入按学历、是否取得执业医师、年级分层分级逐年递增，允许同时填报两个以上志愿，服从调剂。</span></p><p></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"background: white;\">（五）委培学员必须为派送单位在编职工或与单位签订正式聘<span style=\"color:black\">用合同的职工，委培学员培训结束后，学员均回委托培养单位工作，我院不予留用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（六）参培学员应结业当年及之后两年未通过结业考核者，如再次申请结业考核，需重新参加住院医师规范化培训，培训相关费用由个人承担。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（七）奖励性绩效由我院依据相关管理规定发放：奖励性绩效每人每月基数<span>2222</span>元；取得执业医师资格证书后，并在我院注册，每人每月增加发放<span>1000</span>元。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">除以上待遇之外，还享受以下补充待遇：</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">1</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">）免费住宿或专项住宿补贴<span>3</span></span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">00</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">元</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">/</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">月；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">2</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">）伙食补贴<span>36</span></span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">0</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">元</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">/</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">月；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">3</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">）发放国庆、医师节、春节等福利；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">4</span><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">）培训期间各类考核优秀者均按相应标准发放额外奖励。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px 15px 16px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: black; background: white;\">（<span>5</span>）同本院职工一样享受每年一次的体检。</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><br/> </span><strong><span style=\"color: black;\">六、报名：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\">委培学员由派送单位统一报名。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; background: white;\">社会化学员</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">实行现场报名，下载</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">“</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">个人简历</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">”</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">表格，见附件，填写好相关资料后提交纸质档一份和电子档一份，</span><span><a href=\"mailto:%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E6%A1%A3%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%88%B0KJK8915@126.com\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>电子档提交邮箱：</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">KJK8915@126.com</span></a></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">1.</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">报名时间：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">社会化学员：<span>2023</span>年<span>6</span>月<span>1</span>日至<span>2023</span>年<span>6</span>月<span>30</span>日</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">委培学员：<span>2023</span>年<span>6</span>月<span>1</span>日至<span>2023</span>年<span>8</span>月<span>31</span>日</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">2.</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">报名及通讯地址：盐城市第一人民医院 教育处<span>(</span>盐城市毓龙西路<span>166</span>号）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">3.</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">邮编：<span>224006</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">电话：<span>0515</span>—<span>88508935</span></span></