height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">6.近三年内在经营活动中无严重不良记录</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">7</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">.报名截止时间：2023年</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">9</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;月 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">21 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">日 24：00</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">联系人：唐老师&nbsp;&nbsp;联系方式：18921892789&nbsp; </span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">8</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">.具体遴选时间，另行通知。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:27px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">报名表：</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:27px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/attachment/cms/item/2023_09/15_16/af2cd03feed227ce.png.cthumb.jpg\" title=\"5d85ef4b1f53209ad4b4f2596c09bef.png\" alt=\"5d85ef4b1f53209ad4b4f2596c09bef.png\"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'#field_endtime_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'attribute\' => \n  array (\n    6 => 6,\n  ),\n  \'level_time\' => \'权重有效期\',\n  \'level\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'custom_a\' => \'\',\n  \'attachment_pdf\' => \'\',\n  \'config\' => \n  array (\n    \'allow_ip\' => \n    array (\n      \'enabled\' => \'0\',\n      \'collectip\' => \'\',\n      \'area_ip\' => \'\',\n      \'ruleoutip\' => \'\',\n    ),\n  ),\n  \'html\' => \'1\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'1\',\n  \'action\' => \'update\',\n  \'id\' => \'3986\',\n  \'iid\' => \'3986\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'f29251e7ace772de\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'宣传处\',\n  \'verified_flag\' => 0,\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n)','1694765841');
