严格执行请销假和离盐报备制度，未经批假不准离岗。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin-top: 15px;\">6.要保持良好的精神状态，工作、值班期间以及次日有重要任务如手术等不准饮酒，严禁酗酒。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin-top: 15px;\">7.要遵守会风会纪，不准迟到早退、无故缺席。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin-top: 15px;\">8.要自觉抵制不当言论，不准在互联网、微信朋友圈等媒体发布不当言论。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin-top: 15px;\">9.要严格遵守廉洁从业相关规定，不准收“红包”、拿回扣、私自收费、转介患者、违规统方、骗取医保基金等。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin-top: 15px;\">10.要严格遵守法律法规和纪律规定，不准从事赌博、酒驾等违纪违法活动。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'#field_endtime_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'html\' => \'1\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'custom_a\' => \'\',\n  \'level_time\' => \'权重有效期\',\n  \'level\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'attachment_pdf\' => \'\',\n  \'config\' => \n  array (\n    \'allow_ip\' => \n    array (\n      \'enabled\' => \'0\',\n      \'collectip\' => \'\',\n      \'area_ip\' => \'\',\n      \'ruleoutip\' => \'\',\n    ),\n  ),\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'credit_type\' => \'0\',\n  \'credit\' => \'1\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n